self.title: CDISC SEND Implantation Findings Result Terminology

definition: Terminology relevant to the results for implantation findings.
name: Implantation Findings Result
preferredTerm: CDISC SEND Implantation Findings Result Terminology

terms.definition: The absence of life or state of being dead. (NCI)
Death of a conceptus that occurred inside the uterus during the embryonic phase of development, with no recognizable tissue structure.
An implantation site that contains no discernable embryonic or placental tissue but may contain remnants of the implantation.
Death of a conceptus that occurred inside the uterus.
Death of a conceptus that occurred inside the uterus during the fetal phase of development, with recognizable tissue structure.
